<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Classic Hits html email project</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Classic Hits project "/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Classic Hits - Online Music Panel</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Classic Hits</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">As a media brand <a href="http://www.classichits.co.nz/" target="_blank">Classic Hits</a> actively participates in social interactions with their audience. The Classic Hits - Online Music Panel is one such avenue for the brand. It allows fans the chance to vote on their favorite artists and win prizes in the process.</p><p><span class="small-cap">html</span> emails can often be challenging in the limitations they place on development and design so that they don't behave unexpectedly in the various email clients. I've produced many such email templates in my time but for some reason, I still like this one. It's subtly simple but still has a dynamic, graphic style to it that is inline with their other marketing assets.</p><p>It's a little old now but they are still happily using the template.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/classic/image_01_lge.jpg"><div id="project_lg" class="project"><img src="/images/works/projects/classic/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Classic Hits - Music Panel template"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>